{"tid":2344498,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[港女] CLC香港成員Elkie向公司提出解約","createTime":"2020-12-28T18:54:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-28T18:56:59.000Z","uid":224066,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9a616567d33cbc73fb95a20eed76f977dd01ec29","tid":2344498,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T18:54:20.000Z","msg":"韓國女團CLC成員之一嘅Elkie（莊錠欣）係第二位港產韓星，童星出身嘅佢拍過唔少劇集，例如《On Call 36小時II》、《公主嫁到》、《老表你好hea!》及《張保仔》等等。Elkie亦係薛家燕愛徒之一，曾經係Honey Bees成員。2014年當時只有14歲嘅Elkie，突然放低香港學業和演藝事業，遠赴南韓加入Cube娛樂成為旗下練習生。由於Elkie表現唔錯，加入公司短短5至6個月便中途加入女團CLC，成為人氣K-POP女團之一。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Mf9xh7IbDOgbEJ3J9TqyAg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTk2MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-12/9dbc2310-48e7-11eb-9df5-5dcfd13964d4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FMf9xh7IbDOgbEJ3J9TqyAg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-12%2F9dbc2310-48e7-11eb-9df5-5dcfd13964d4&h=5144d850&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近日爆出佢向經理人公司CUBE娛樂公司提出解約消息，有指CUBE多次違約，指出Elkie過去4年間被公司拖糧等問題。Elkie指演藝收入都係由公司收取，但從未向佢披露收入細節；各種演唱會及商演都冇收入，佢只收過版稅收入。 另外，公司亦向CLC表明唔會再支持組合發展，因此提出解約。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Zy6hr.ePQlCZAxwJsQGaKQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUyMi44OTM2MTcwMjEyNzY2/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-12/fd6899d0-48ea-11eb-a73f-58f89af3921a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FZy6hr.ePQlCZAxwJsQGaKQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUyMi44OTM2MTcwMjEyNzY2%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-12%2Ffd6899d0-48ea-11eb-a73f-58f89af3921a&h=70b472ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/uqonFYkDEPQJ3sgPrt993g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTEzNTcuOTEzMDQzNDc4MjYwOA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-12/156e4f30-48ea-11eb-9567-b5a42c4e0e9e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FuqonFYkDEPQJ3sgPrt993g--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTEzNTcuOTEzMDQzNDc4MjYwOA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-12%2F156e4f30-48ea-11eb-9567-b5a42c4e0e9e&h=57816787&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/mrOy6FLg.hX7YKpd.N4TPA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTEzNDguMTczOTEzMDQzNDc4Mw--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-12/273b31b0-48ea-11eb-b05f-c4c8004e2e2d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FmrOy6FLg.hX7YKpd.N4TPA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTEzNDguMTczOTEzMDQzNDc4Mw--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-12%2F273b31b0-48ea-11eb-b05f-c4c8004e2e2d&h=d6b8e7d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nElkie透過北京嘅京師律師事務發出律師信，要求CUBE娛樂需要係15日內交出4年間嘅所有收入細節，並須支付所有演藝收入，否則將會進行提告。CUBE娛樂公司到今日都未有作出回應，而Elkie亦無透露解約之後會去邊到發展。"},{"pid":"7818d4422b25cb13bb15f257af7ec0cbce4dbbd1","tid":2344498,"uid":215755,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T18:56:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/UnlawfulHeartyChanticleer-size_restricted.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FUnlawfulHeartyChanticleer-size_restricted.gif&h=cf75d4f5&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}